# 🔌 Python Socket Chat Project

This project demonstrates a basic implementation of socket programming in Python. It includes a simple TCP client and server that can exchange text messages over a local network.

---

## 🛠️ Features

- TCP connection using `socket` module
- Client sends messages to the server
- Server responds to client messages
- Graceful shutdown with `Ctrl+C`

---

